      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a smooth and dependable ride that you'll love. The interior is clean and comfortable, making every journey a pleasure. It's a reliable choice that's ready for its next adventure!",
