      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Slide into a lost era of automotive perfection. This isn\u2019t just a vehicle; it\u2019s a time capsule preserved in liquid amber. The paint captures the sunlight like a polished gemstone, while the interior whispers tales of luxury with leather so supple it feels like a second skin. Every curve of the bodywork tells a story of meticulous care and weekend escapes where the road never ended. To drive this machine is to command a symphony of engineering excellence, a rare gem that has escaped the ravages of time to wait, poised and breathless, for its next curator.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
